To install, clone the repository and add the following to your init
file:

	(load-file "/path/to/tamil99.el")

To activate the input method, say C-u C-\ tamil99 RET.

If you have any comments or improvements to be made, please write to
the Author's mail mentioned in the file.

[ NOTE: This repository is only a placeholder until I get enough
  feedback and will be added to an Emacs release, and as such, any
  significant contributions will require copyright assignment to the
  FSF.  You can get the CA form by mailing emacs-devel.  ]
